    <item>
      <title>Build your homepage using Blowfish and Hugo</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/guides/202310-blowfish-tutorial/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Oct 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>contact@urai-group.com (URAI)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/guides/202310-blowfish-tutorial/</guid>
      <description>Just one year ago, I created Blowfish, a Hugo theme crafted to build my unique vision for my personal homepage. I also decided to make it an open-source project. Fast-forward to today, and Blowfish has transformed into a thriving open-source project with over 600 stars on GitHub and a user base of hundreds. In this tutorial, I’ll show you how to get started and have your website running in a couple of minutes.</description>
